{"tid":628987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譴責六四屠城 中共密友斯諾遺孀逝世","createTime":"2018-04-14T10:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T10:48:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d55517a651edab4d65d54e03c6be8176f5740da6","tid":628987,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180414/20361038?_ga=2.8096434.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361038%3F_ga%3D2.8096434.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=y2KIXyCTZjw%2B5kY2bIgPDxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=bb6df31c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361038%3F_ga%3D2.8096434.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=53f89659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180414/20361038?_ga=2.8096434.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n譴責六四屠城<br />\n中共密友斯諾遺孀逝世<br />\n<br />\n4.2K<br />\n國際新聞<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/14wx05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2F14wx05p.jpg&h=2a8fdee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斯諾與洛伊絲（左一及右一）1970年訪華，兩人在天安門城樓與毛澤東交談。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與中共關係友好的美國已故記者埃德加．斯諾（Edgar Snow）遺孀、自六四事件後抨擊中國人權狀況的洛伊絲（Lois Wheeler Snow），上周二在瑞士尼翁一間醫院逝世，享年97歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天安門城樓與毛交談<br />\n<br />\n洛伊絲本是紐約百老匯演員，1949年成為斯諾第二任妻子。斯諾1936年身赴延安，成為首位採訪中共領袖的西方記者，著作《紅星照耀中國》因頌揚中共而聞名，與毛澤東、周恩來等中共第一代領袖友好。當時美國處於麥卡錫時代，斯諾夫婦因通共而被列入黑名單，自此移居瑞士。<br />\n<br />\n洛伊絲自言邂逅斯諾後，中國就成為其生命一部份。她在1970年隨夫首次訪華，兩人在天安門城樓與毛澤東交談的一幕，被視為中共想與美國復交的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n斯諾1972年去世後，洛伊絲亦頻頻訪華，但她直言在1989年天安門屠城後清醒過來，選擇譴責鎮壓並拒再踏足中國，改為借斯諾之名，致函中國領導人要求善待示威者遺屬。直至2000年，洛伊絲才再次到北京為亡夫掃墓，卻無法探訪天安門母親丁子霖，洛伊絲此後再無踏足中國。 <br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/14wx06p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2F14wx06p.jpg&h=1302e222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洛伊絲"},{"pid":"eded1e53dd2f4bae5ddccc38a56ff66efbd3a579","tid":628987,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39b436402d684d70c8381a16d6d27bd6b76e2b94","tid":628987,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:42:36.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31058b44cf644b2d2ea33d47ec9b7007db6e735e","tid":628987,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}